space.world

Class Beam

  • java.lang.Object
    • space.world.Entity
      • space.world.NonStationary
        • space.world.Beam
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ViewableBeam, ViewableNonStationary, ViewableObject

    public class Beam
extends NonStationary
implements ViewableBeam
    Represents a laser beam which has been shot out of a BeamShooter. It shuts off a turret if the beam collides with the turret.
    Author:
    Maria Libunao
